      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 power plant features a meticulously maintained Vanos system and updated rod bearings, delivering linear torque and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission is paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis is structurally flawless, benefiting from a reinforced subframe and pristine bushings to maintain original suspension kinematics. Garage-kept with original paint, this vehicle exhibits no mechanical or aesthetic degradation, offering a pure, analog driving experience.",
